Huangdi Bashiyi Nanjing (Chinese: 黃帝八十一難經; lit
'The Huang Emperor's Canon of Eighty-One Difficult Issues'), nke a na-akpọkarịri Nan Jing, bụ otu n'ime ọgwụ ọdịnala ndị China (TCM)

A chịkọtara Nan Jing na China n'oge narị afọ mbụ O.A., a na-akpọ Nan Jin n"ihi na isi iri asato na otu ya na'ịchọ ịkọwapụta nkwupụta dị mgbagwoju anya e mere na Huangdi Neijing ma jiri ya mee ihe nke ukwuu maka ọmụmụ na ntụaka na Japanese acupuncture na ọgwụ ọdịnala Japanese (TJM).
